Document: RootMotionView
Path: godot/classes/class_rootmotionview.rst
Summary: Properties and their default values for the RootMotionView class.

- Property: animation_path (NodePath): The path to the animation resource. Default: NodePath("")
- Property: cell_size (float): Size of each cell in the grid display. Default: 1.0
- Property: color (Color): Color used for visual representation. Default: Color(0.5, 0.5, 1, 1)
- Property: radius (float): Radius of the motion visualization circle. Default: 10.0
- Property: zero_y (bool): Whether to constrain motion to the Y=0 plane. Default: true
